data.description: Huge Price Improvement! Don’t wait to come and experience country living in a small town. BIG trees, red farmhouse, tin roof, huge backyard AND a 30 x 7 front porch. This property is for the visionary, the romance of a fixer upper farmhouse or the investor expanding a rental portfolio. The 3 BR 1 BA home features an open living and dining arrangement. The galley kitchen has a window over the sink, nice light, stove plumbed for propane or electric! 2 BR, 1 Bath on main level with claw foot tub, 3rd is an expansive loft upstairs.  LVP flooring on lower level. With a 0.22 acre lot, the backyard is huge, with potential to be the entertaining space, have animals and gardens of your dreams. Less than 30 minutes to Sherman or McKinney, less than 10 to Bonham. Price point established for flexibility in giving this charmer its best life.
